  - Header: SharedSpacesApplication
    Description: "This is the entry point for the whole Shared Spaces application.
      It initializes the application's core at startup and loads the application
      state controller and handlers. Additionally, it exposes these controllers and
      handlers for use throughout the application. \n\nIt also fetches the player
      state upon login and manages join intent.\r"
    Reference:
      m_referenceType: 5
      m_obj: {fileID: 0}
      m_classType: 
      m_scene: {fileID: 102900000, guid: 546a900b29a296a43b765f4d751a96f0, type: 3}
      m_name: SharedSpacesApplication
      m_path: 
      m_guid: 
      m_instanceID: 0
  - Header: SharedSpacesNetworkLayer
    Description: This manages network connections using both the Unity Netcode API
      and Photon connections. It also handles user connection, reconnection, and
      disconnection. Additionally, it registers for callbacks to manage various events
      during the connection process.
